channel.title: Beste private server?

I tryed searching but most of the ones that look good have broken download links so if anyone helped me find a server thats not too bad on lagg, has decent minigames, a good amount of npc's and more recent items i would really really appreciate the help locating it. {My grammar isn't too well and I'mm sorry for that.}
